        in proc. 28th annual simulation
    symposium, phoenix, az, april 1995.  also available as tr 533,
  computer science department, university of rochester, september
  1994.

 r. bianchini, m. e. crovella, l. i. kontothanassis, and t. j. leblanc.
         ``software interleaving.'' 
        in proc., 6th spdp, dallas, tx, ocober 1994.
 r. j. fowler and l. i. kontothanassis.
         ``mercury: object-affinity scheduling and continuation passing on multiprocessors'' 
        in proc., parle '94, athens, greece, june 1994.
 r. w. wisniewski, l. i. kontothanassis, and m. l. scott.
         ``scalable spin locks for multiprogrammed systems''  
        in proc., 8th ipps, cancun mexico, april 1994.
 l. kontothanassis and r. wisniewski
         ``using scheduler information to achieve optimal barrier synchronization performance.''    
        in proc., 4th ppopp, san diego, ca, may 1993.
 w. e. garrett, m. l. scott, r. bianchini, l. i. kontothanassis, 
r. a. mccallum, j. a. thomas, r. wisniewski, s. luk
