        in proc. of the usenix winter '93 technical conference,
        san diego, ca, january 1993.
 r. j. fowler and l. i. kontothanassis
         ``supporting user-level exception handling on a multiprocessor micro-kernel: experiences with platinum'' 
        in proc., 3rd sedms, newport beach, ca, march 1992



